You were not just a friend — you were also my very first client.

In this vast world, I never imagined that the first person to believe in me would be both my closest friend and my very first client. You weren’t just there at the start — you were the start. Your trust gave my dream its first breath.

From the very first step of this journey, you’ve been by my side — cheering, guiding, and holding space for every hope and hurdle. Now, watching you and Bhavya step into this new chapter together feels like witnessing a beautiful promise unfold.

From the bottom of my heart, thank you. You didn’t just support a business; you gave VowStories its name, its life, and its soul. The memories we’ve created will forever be written in the story of VowStories.

@bhavya.mehta_spt — please treasure her always. She is one of the purest souls I know, and she’ll always carry a piece of my heart wherever life takes her.

From your forever sister at VowStories, with endless love, to @surnimilan 

Thank you for trusting us — your faith and love are the true fulfillment of everything we dreamed of creating.
